<div class="mt-3 marketing" style="overflow: hidden; padding: 20px;">
  <hr class="featurette-divider">
  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <%= image_tag 'teste.jpeg', class: 'img-fluid', alt: 'Descrição da imagem' %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="mt-5" style="overflow: hidden;">
        <h2 class="mb-4">WHAT WE OFFERING</h2>

        <div class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
          <%= image_tag 'icon_1.png', alt: 'Descrição da imagem', class: 'img-fluid', style: 'width: 70px; height: 70px;' %>
          <div class="ms-3">
            <p class="fw-bold mb-1">Office Cleaning</p>
            <p class="text-justify" style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;">
              Keeping an office clean is important for a healthy and productive work environment. Regular cleaning of desks, floors, and common areas helps reduce germs and keeps the space looking professional. A clean office makes a good impression on clients and improves employee well-being.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
          <%= image_tag 'icon_2.png', alt: 'Descrição da imagem', class: 'img-fluid', style: 'width: 70px; height: 70px;' %>
          <div class="ms-3">
            <p class="fw-bold mb-1">House Cleaning</p>
            <p class="text-justify" style="text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;">
              Are you tired of working and taking care of everything yourself? Don't worry anymore, we have the best House Cleaning Service in Columbus. We take care of your home with dedication and responsibility for you. Now you can have more time for yourself. Schedule a free quote now. <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #03285E;">(614) 592-8665</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 text-center">
          <%= link_to 'Discover Services', servicos_path, class: 'btn btn-primary', style: 'background-color: #03285E; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;' %>
          <div class="icon">
            <div class="vector"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
